# Fetched third-party corpus binaries are NEVER committed — they are pulled by
# scripts/fetch_corpus.py (pinned SHA-256, license-gated) into vroid/ per the
# manifest's `candidates`. Only license-verified, redistribution-clear assets are
# vendored, and those live under spec-samples/ (tracked, not matched here).
vroid/**/*.vrm
vroid/**/*.glb
vroid/**/*.vrm.part

# Local scratch imports produced while inspecting corpus assets.
**/*.usda.local
